      "content": "it's not just chaos though. it's like, they deserve a version of life that isn't defined by my failures. if i'm gone, they don't have to worry about me, they don't have to feel guilty for me, and they can just... start fresh. don't you think sometimes that the most selfless thing a person can do is just stop being a burden to the people they love?",
